oai_dc:dc.dc:description: This paper presents the results of studies carried out by ARTELIA for the intake and outfall system of the new Shoaiba II thermal power plant, on behalf of DAELIM. These studies included hydraulic desk studies, thermal dispersion simulation study, physical model tests and simulation study of ship manoeuvring for the fuel oil terminal.
